data.description: DOUBLE YOUR PLEASURE and YOUR INCOME POTENTIAL!  Over Two Acres of Terrific Commercial Frontage on Highway 71, the major highway through Mena, Arkansas between Ft. Smith and Texarkana.  Superb visibility for any business. The BONUS is a lovely 4 bedroom, two bath, one half bath 2,656 sq ft home located on the back of the acreage for convenience to business, and offering gracious country living.  Formal living room with open concept into dining and kitchen areas, spacious den with gas log fireplace, separate office, huge master suite with walk-in closet and private bath, laundry, three more bedrooms, one full and one half bath. Original wood flooring plus caperting.  The house has two decks and one covered porch,  Two car carport.  Two HVAC units. 24x30 Shop with concrete floors and 220 service.  Ample storage inside and out.  Upgrades completed over the last 5 years including new roof. new windows, new water heater, new meter loop, and fresh paint.  Agents please see Showing Instructions.
